imdb.plot outline: LAnzate features the dynamic Fernanda Kelly and Luis Sandoval, who present bold, fast-paced content and unique interactive opportunities for Hispanic millennials or "billennials" at interesting locations throughout Los Angeles, Miami, Chicago, and Mexico City. The premiere marked the first time that a Univision Network entertainment program was produced in Los Angeles.
